      <section class="type-scale">
        <h1>Type scale</h1>
        <p>This type scale uses custom properties for a responsive major-second ratio.</p>
        <dl>
          <dt style="font-size: var(--font-size--2)">Aa</dt>
          <dd>--font-size--2</dd>
          <dt style="font-size: var(--font-size--1)">Aa</dt>
          <dd>--font-size--1</dd>
          <dt style="font-size: var(--font-size-0)">Aa</dt>
          <dd>--font-size-0</dd>
          <dt style="font-size: var(--font-size-1)">Aa</dt>
          <dd>--font-size-1</dd>
          <dt style="font-size: var(--font-size-2)">Aa</dt>
          <dd>--font-size-2</dd>
          <dt style="font-size: var(--font-size-3)">Aa</dt>
          <dd>--font-size-3</dd>
          <dt style="font-size: var(--font-size-4)">Aa</dt>
          <dd>--font-size-4</dd>
          <dt style="font-size: var(--font-size-5)">Aa</dt>
          <dd>--font-size-5</dd>
          <dt style="font-size: var(--font-size-6)">Aa</dt>
          <dd>--font-size-6</dd>
          <dt style="font-size: var(--font-size-7)">Aa</dt>
          <dd>--font-size-7</dd>
        </dl>

        <section class="sample-content">
          <h1>SEI connects classrooms, campuses, and communities</h1>
          <p>SEI leads faculty professional development and curriculum innovation in sustainability and environmental education across the district. Our work
            bridges operations and learning, turning campus construction and facilities into living laboratories for students.</p>

          <h2>Programs &amp; Learning</h2>
          <p>Through workshops, coaching, and the Demonstration Project, SEI supports educators in embedding environmental equity into every discipline—from
            political science to English. Faculty gain practical tools, shared resources, and a community of practice committed to authentic climate education.
          </p>

          <h3>Student Opportunities</h3>
          <p>With partners like Build LACCD, SEI has helped expand internships from nine to more than one hundred across the district. These applied experiences
            connect classroom learning to real jobs, advancing equitable access to sustainability careers.</p>

          <blockquote>“Because of SEI, new campus construction is now part of the classroom—turning buildings and operations into living labs for
            sustainability.”</blockquote>

          <p>Beyond the district, SEI collaborates with universities, Indigenous communities, and local partners to align policy, practice, and public
            engagement—so that climate learning leads to durable change.</p>
        </section>

      </section>

